  <brief_title>MODULA-Study: Modul 10: Benefit of CRT-Therapy in CRT-Patients With QRS-Complex of 120 - 150 Ms</brief_title>
  <official_title>MODULA-Study: Modul 10: Benefit of CRT-therapy in CRT-Patients With QRS-complex of 120 - 150 ms</official_title>
