  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with cardiac resynchronization therapy with a defibrillator (CRT-D) or
             cardiac resynchronization therapy pacemakers (CRT-P) system

          -  New York Heart Association (NYHA) III

          -  Ejection fraction (EF) below 35%

          -  Optimised medical therapy

          -  QRS-complex above 120 ms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with CRT-P and atrial fibrillation
      </textblock>
